---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Breadcrumb from "../components/Breadcrumb.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service | doticrosst" description="Terms of service for doticrosst website design and SEO services. Payment terms, intellectual property and liability." noindex={true}>
  <section class="pt-12 pb-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: "Home", href: "/" }, { label: "Terms of Service" }]} />
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal sm:text-5xl">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Last updated: March 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-32 border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="space-y-10">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Agreement</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            By accessing doticrosst.com, you agree to these terms of service. If you do not
            agree with any part of these terms, please do not use this website. These terms
            apply to all visitors, users, and clients of doticrosst.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Services</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            doticrosst provides digital agency services including website design, local SEO,
            and ongoing website support for small businesses. We also operate a specialist
            division for hairdressers and barbers. Specific terms for individual projects,
            including scope of work, pricing, timelines, and deliverables, are agreed in
            writing before any work begins.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            Quotes provided through our scoping form or by email are valid for 30 days from
            the date of issue. Project timelines are estimates and may vary depending on
            client responsiveness and the complexity of the work. We will communicate any
            changes to agreed timelines promptly.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Payment terms</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            Payment terms are agreed on a per-project basis and outlined in your project
            quote. Typically, we require a deposit before work begins with the balance due
            on completion and before the website goes live. We accept bank transfer and
            other standard payment methods. Late payments may result in suspension of
            ongoing support services.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Intellectual property</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            Upon full payment, clients own the deliverables created for their project,
            including website code, content, and design assets. doticrosst retains the right
            to use anonymised examples of completed work in our portfolio and marketing
            materials unless otherwise agreed in writing. Third-party assets such as fonts,
            stock images, or software libraries remain subject to their respective licences.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Client responsibilities</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            Clients are responsible for providing accurate information, content, images, and
            feedback in a timely manner. Delays caused by late provision of materials may
            affect project timelines. Clients are responsible for ensuring they have the
            rights to any content or images they provide for use on their website.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Hosting and domain</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            Websites built by doticrosst are hosted on Netlify, which provides free hosting
            for the traffic levels most small businesses generate. Clients are responsible
            for their own domain name registration and renewal. We can assist with domain
            setup and DNS configuration as part of the project scope.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Ongoing support</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            Optional ongoing support plans are available on a monthly basis. Support plans
            can be cancelled at any time with 30 days notice. Support covers content
            updates, performance monitoring, and technical maintenance as described in
            your support agreement.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Limitation of liability</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            doticrosst provides services on an "as is" basis. We are not liable for any
            indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from use of our services
            or this website. Our total liability for any claim related to our services is
            limited to the amount paid for the specific service in question. We do not
            guarantee specific search engine rankings, traffic levels, or business outcomes.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Governing law</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            These terms are governed by the laws of England and Wales. Any disputes arising
            from these terms or our services will be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction
            of the courts of England and Wales.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Changes</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            We may update these terms of service from time to time. The date at the top
            of this page shows when these terms were last revised. Continued use of the
            website after changes are published constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Contact</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            Questions about these terms? Email
            <a href="mailto:craig@doticrosst.com" class="font-medium text-charcoal hover:text-charcoal-light">craig@doticrosst.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
